{"tid":315264,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"《香港獨立論》讀書會","createTime":"2017-07-10T01:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T11:37:17.000Z","uid":92301,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5d2b044e9e257b7a25e6ba128025d2e3562f1e","tid":315264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T01:28:34.000Z","msg":"本土民主前線將於7月15日舉行讀書會，討論梁衍華著作《香港獨立論》。獨派過往一直被指欠缺論述基礎，難以說服乃至動員群眾。作為獨派一員，實有必要整理獨立論述脈絡，並以游說港人為己任。<br />\n<br />\n活動名額20至25人，歡迎<span style=\"color: red;\">有興趣人士透過私訊本土民主前線FB專頁報名參加。</span><br />\n<br />\n《香港獨立論》讀書會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：7月15日（六）<br />\n時間：下午3時<br />\n地點：火炭</span>（確認報名後將有專人通知）<br />\n<br />\n（以下為《香港獨立論》簡介，轉載自 <a href=\"http://www.hkaps.com.hk/NewRelease.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkaps.com.hk%2FNewRelease.html&d=FT5iXao0TO42acrCgIi6pzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=663eb989\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkaps.com.hk/NewRelease.html</a><br />\n<br />\n// 長久以來，香港主權獨立是一個近乎無人觸及的議題。在開始深入探討該議題前，大部份人已經武斷地否定了主權獨立的可能。本書分為法律篇、古代史篇、近代史篇、當代篇、文化篇及生存篇共六個篇章，嘗試以學術角度去分析香港主權獨立及相關事項。<br />\n<br />\n法律篇以國際法角度探討香港主權獨立是否具有法理依據為開端，再揭示有關的法理基礎與香港是否具有獨立歷史及文化的相關性。古代史篇及近代史篇探討香港是否有異於華夏的歷史觀。當代篇則探討因為沒有獨立主權而在當代面對的問題。文化篇探討粵漢文化之別、香港文化異於華夏及粵英混合的特點。生存篇將假設香港作為一個主權獨立國家，將會面對的生存威脅，以及其他國家面對有關威脅時所採取的應對手段。//）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1929088197345083&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=1546925482228025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1929088197345083%26substory_index%3D0%26id%3D1546925482228025&d=FT5iXao0TO42acrCgIi6pzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a7617e90\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1929088197345083&amp;substory_index=0&amp;id=1546925482228025</a>"},{"pid":"a9cf3f44f986f1c95a1fb2286a5d664748f67381","tid":315264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5f0bf0b44314632545d7f99dc6b9c23f4055e9","tid":315264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa4467c1372007aeb6cf96089493debaa26a656","tid":315264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c474e87383d886bf51f27181dde6c4e14e29e983","tid":315264,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d012c267ee1386a19c7350e8bd03e33ec9b3d1","tid":315264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e78343fe4947ecf208c4c65d0cffa0c889df16","tid":315264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99dc7954cc5ed7762e8ef8b172f37eeba828e13d","tid":315264,"uid":6263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"本野邊度有得賣"},{"pid":"8066408230c7bd07a0164ec7f5cf40520651bc4c","tid":315264,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b2c7024245f3d41a75ff414bec758df5779e7d","tid":315264,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本野邊度有得賣</blockquote><br />\nthis <a href=\"http://www.